fields.customfield_16601:
As part of Integration Guardians testing requirements, the following tests under load are required:
Initial Install  to 17.6
Upgrade 17.5->17.6 under load
Rollback
Upgrade from an ISO with the resize included to another 17.6 ISO

No new RPMs are required.
Deployment Description XML Changes are only required:
db_postgres_fs=8G,20G,24G,32G

fields.customfield_16601:
Added the TMS links for the tests we are going to perform for a single node,the same will be done for 960 nodes.There will not by any sync of nodes done as part of our tests.However ,nodes should be in sync state for us to start our tests.

The following netsim patches are to be installed 
http://netsim.lmera.ericsson.se/tssweb/patches/P05965.zip


Also script  SelectedandSupportedCiphers_COMECIM script to be run which is available at https://confluence-nam.lmera.ericsson.se/display/Abhedya/Netsim+patch+process+for+Cipher+Modernization

DG2 nodes will be restarted twice ,one after patch installation and other after script execution.

Can you let us know when we can get the server to perform our tests.

Thanks,
Sri Deepthi
